description:
Video Producer Owen Poole puts the high-tech "Hyperboots" to the test in this episode of Prove It. A collaboration between Hyperice and Nike, the Hyperboots are designed to help athletes warm up, recover and train better thanks to a combination of heat and compression. They're loved by pro-level athletes, but can an amateur distance runner get any benefit from the tech?
